title: Panthers Raise Money at Annual Prowl (University of Wisconsin - Milwaukee)
text: ( Source : University of Wisconsin - Milwaukee ) Students, families and alumni gathered Saturday morning for the 11th annual Panther Prowl - followed by the unveiling of the new Panther statue in front of Enderis Hall . Supporters cheered
